          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Senior Scams Prevention Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a Senior Scams Prevention Advisory Council, which shall create&nbsp;model educational materials to&nbsp;educate&nbsp;employees of&nbsp;retailers, financial-services companies,&nbsp;and wire-transfer companies on how to identify and prevent scams that affect seniors. </p>]]></text>
